1.3 The Three Decision Review Pathways}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af4\loch\ql\widctlpar\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\ql\widctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\f4\fs24\lang1033\kerning0\dbch\af7\langfe2052\sb0\sa120{\loch
Under the Appeals Modernization Act (AMA), Veterans have three options when they disagree with a VA decision:}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af4\loch\ql\widctlpar\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\ql\widctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\f4\fs24\lang1033\kerning0\dbch\af7\langfe2052\sb0\sa200\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af4\loch\ql\widctlpar\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\ql\widctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\f4\fs24\lang1033\kerning0\dbch\af7\langfe2052\sb0\sa120{\rtlch\ab \ltrch\loch\b\loch
1. Supplemental Claim}{\loch
 \u8212\'97 Add new and relevant evidence to support the claim. VA will help gather evidence. Average processing: ~125 days.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af4\loch\ql\widctlpar\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\ql\widctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\f4\fs24\lang1033\kerning0\dbch\af7\langfe2052\sb0\sa120{\rtlch\ab \ltrch\loch\b\loch
2. Higher-Level Review (HLR)}{\loch
 \u8212\'97 Request a senior reviewer examine the existing record for errors. No new evidence allowed. Average processing: ~125 days.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af4\loch\ql\widctlpar\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\ql\widctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\f4\fs24\lang1033\kerning0\dbch\af7\langfe2052\sb0\sa120{\rtlch\ab \ltrch\loch\b\loch
3. Board Appeal}{\loch
 \u8212\'97 Have a Veterans Law Judge review the case. Three docket options: Direct Review, Evidence Submission, or Hearing. Average processing: ~365+ days.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af4\loch\ql\widctlpar\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\ql\widctlpar\hyphpar0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\f4\fs24\lang1033\kerning0\dbch\af7\langfe2052\sb100\sa100\cbpat26{\rtlch\ai \ltrch\loch\i\loch
